data.description: Impeccable 2-bed, 2-bath Stonewall home, move-in ready! Ideal for families or short-term rental investment, nestled on the prestigious 290 wine trail. No carpets. Savor Texas sunsets on covered porches or guest house balcony. Guest House boasts a bedroom, kitchen, and full bath downstairs, with a living room area on the main level. Add your personal touch for a charming retreat. Don't miss this opportunity!
